# Architecture Synchronization & Optimization Plan

This implementation plan outlines the structural, caching, and synchronization enhancements to stabilize the digital library system between the mobile app (React Native), web app (Next.js), backend API (Node.js Express), local mobile database (SQLite), and server database (MySQL). 

All changes will be implemented **without changing any existing business logic, UI layouts, database relationships, authorization controls, or role hierarchies.**

